title: 404 System Failure Portal
description: This is an 404 portal for the upcoming hackathon conducted by GDGoC IET DAVV. It is based on Stranger Things Theme. It includes a small fun game and will display a meme on successfully completion of the game.

title: Cloud study jams leaderboard
description: Unorganised excel data shifted to an organized leaderboard and ease of access to view and track skill badges for participants of cloud study jams.

title: GDG IET latest Website
description: The official GDGoC IET DAVV website, with a custom admin panel for seamless content management of events, projects, and club information.

title: IET Connect App
description: IET Connect App is a one stop platform for students, bringing together all college resources in one place. From notes and syllabi to events and updates, it simplifies campus life with easy, organized access.

title: Vent Chase Among Us Game
description: Vent Chase, an HTML5 game where players, as the last surviving crewmate, must pursue a saboteur through a spaceship's vents. The game features a branching narrative and a secure, token-based reward system.

title: Automated Event Ticketing & Attendance System
description: A comprehensive, dual-backend system for seamless event management. The primary Python backend automates ticket generation. The secondary backend serves a React Native mobile app for scanning tickets.

title: Certificate Automation
description: An automated system that generates and manages personalized event certificates using Excel data and templates.

title: Online Quiz & Examination Platform
description: Platform developed for student selection for AI/ML Workshops. Allows uploading questions in PDF/JSON, tracking cheating attempts, flexible timers, and logging results to Google Sheets.

title: Websprint Website
description: The official event platform for the WebSprint competition organized by GDGOC IET DAVV.

title: Treasure In The Shell
description: Event submission platform featuring a dynamic admin panel with realtime updation of team's entries for the contest.

title: Red Light Green Light Squid Game
description: A fun Red Light Green Light game inspired by Squid Game, built as an engaging activity for students.

title: GDSC Old Website
description: The initial website of GDSC IET DAVV, has collection of all previous resources and informations.
